title: the kingship, the heaven of the pharaoh
description:
This document describes the KINGSHIP OF THE PHARAOH.
every soul who has given their soul to the pharaoh receives
a new souldisk from the pharaoh gods and lives onboard the kingship.

when the pharaoh dies, he boards the kingship and sets sail to the star system of andromeda to the heaven of my father god.


the kingship can kill hell and the devil.
